prediction.sparql:
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?person ?nonAdultTitle WHERE {
  ?person imdb:profession "actor" .
  ?person imdb:knownForTitle ?adultTitle .
  ?adultTitle imdb:isAdult true .
  ?person imdb:knownForTitle ?nonAdultTitle .
  ?nonAdultTitle imdb:isAdult false .
  ?nonAdultTitle imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes >= 100000 )
}
GROUP BY ?person ?nonAdultTitle
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?adultTitle ) >= 3 )
LIMIT 50

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?series ( GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT ?seriesLabel ; SEPARATOR = " | " ) AS ?labels ) ( MAX( ?runtime ) - MIN( ?runtime ) AS ?runtimeDiff ) ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?episode ) AS ?numEpisodes ) ?votes WHERE {
  ?series imdb:type "tvSeries" .
  ?series imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes > 100000 ) OPTIONAL {
    ?series rdfs:label ?seriesLabel
  }
  ?episode imdb:type "tvEpisode" .
  ?episode imdb:parentTitle ?series .
  ?episode imdb:runtimeMinutes ?runtime .
}
GROUP BY ?series ?votes
ORDER BY DESC ( ?runtimeDiff )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?genre ( COUNT( ?movie ) AS ?frequency ) ( AVG( ?rating ) AS ?averageRating ) WHERE {
  ?movie imdb:genre ?genre .
  ?movie imdb:averageRating ?rating .
}
GROUP BY ?genre
ORDER BY DESC ( ?frequency )
